text: Deviant most commonly refers to deviant behavior, particularly in relation to social norms. Deviant may also refer to: * Deviant (comics), a fictional race of humanity in the Marvel Comics' universe * Deviant logic, a class of non- classical logics * "Deviant" (CSI: Miami episode) * A member of the DeviantArt online community ==Music== * Deviant Records, an inactive trance music record label * Deviant (Pitchshifter album), 2000 * Deviant (Regurgitate album), 2003 == See also == * The Deviants (disambiguation) * Deviance (disambiguation) * Deviation (disambiguation)
title: Deviant (disambiguation)
